We can extend these considerations to include  gauge theories
coupled to hypermultiplets in 5 dimensions. In that case we obtain a
one-dimensional gauge theory with matter fields. Now we can no longer
reduce to zero-modes and we get an honest quantum mechanical
system. For example, a five-dimensional gauge theory coupled to a set
of hypermultiplets, that we write in terms of 4d chiral multiplets as
